1
00:00:00,726 --> 00:00:02,106
EXTERMINATE!

2
00:00:03,820 --> 00:00:05,886
SEEK, LOCATE, DESTROY!

3
00:00:13,835 --> 00:00:14,641
What was that thing?

4
00:00:14,666 --> 00:00:15,242
A Dalek.

5
00:00:15,267 --> 00:00:16,102
A what?

6
00:00:16,653 --> 00:00:17,168
A Dalek.

7
00:00:17,193 --> 00:00:18,193
What's a Dalek?

8
00:00:18,596 --> 00:00:20,183
Never mind. It's a Dalek.

9
00:00:20,208 --> 00:00:21,208
Well, that's not explaining.

10
00:00:22,016 --> 00:00:23,290
That's just saying a word.

11
00:00:23,315 --> 00:00:24,315
What's a Dalek?

12
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,586
It's an alien war machine.

13
00:00:28,052 --> 00:00:30,052
The deadliest alien war machine ever devised.

14
00:00:34,106 --> 00:00:35,106
Fat, though.

15
00:00:35,186 --> 00:00:36,186
Sorry.

16
00:00:36,553 --> 00:00:38,553
We'll never get through that door. It's too wide.

17
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:43,920
It's a tank.

18
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:46,323
A tank driven by a super evolved mutant

19
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:48,676
programmed to wipe out all other life forms.

20
00:00:48,701 --> 00:00:50,701
So please, keep your voice down.

21
00:00:53,746 --> 00:00:55,364
It's got a sucker on it.

22
00:00:55,389 --> 00:00:56,389
It's also got a gun.

23
00:00:56,725 --> 00:00:58,064
Well, it's got a gun and a sucker.

24
00:00:58,089 --> 00:00:58,931
Why?

25
00:00:58,956 --> 00:00:59,897
They run out of guns.

26
00:00:59,922 --> 00:01:00,922
Now, please.

27
00:01:01,179 --> 00:01:03,111
Is there a Dalek at the back with no gun and two suckers

28
00:01:03,136 --> 00:01:04,891
and he's really hacked off?

29
00:01:06,133 --> 00:01:07,077
I don't know.

30
00:01:07,102 --> 00:01:08,064
I've never asked

31
00:01:08,089 --> 00:01:11,089
because I've always been too busy running away.

32
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,359
No, please.

33
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,920
One more question.

34
00:01:19,233 --> 00:01:20,963
Oh, you do surprise me.

35
00:01:20,988 --> 00:01:23,716
Why do they keep saying exterminate?

36
00:01:25,386 --> 00:01:26,803
Because they want to kill us.

37
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,480
Wouldn't it be quicker to just say kill?

38
00:01:29,746 --> 00:01:31,746
Do we really want them to save time?

39
00:01:32,807 --> 00:01:33,807
Good point.

40
00:01:35,773 --> 00:01:36,773
Oh, no.

41
00:01:37,133 --> 00:01:38,000
We need to get back.

42
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Back where?

43
00:01:39,705 --> 00:01:40,705
To the future.

44
00:01:41,273 --> 00:01:43,022
2017 needs us.

45
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,000
EXTERMINATE!

46
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
NEW ANOTHER LIFE DETECTED.

